caption: Amazingly, by Saturday morning, all signs of the impromptu Roadkill Nights drag strip were removed and normal traffic returned to Woodward Avenue. Plans for 2017 are unknown. It is possible this was a once in a lifetime event. We're glad to have witnessed it!
